{
  "page": "Feature quote/48",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Men are such faithless creatures.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> <br />“Who’s the traitor today?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a><br />“So much villainy, it sings a sad song for our age. Did honor die with our fathers?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a><br />“<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">My father</a> is not dead yet.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 49\">Chapter 49</a>, Tyrion XI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404102034\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 81/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8420/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 301/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 525/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.461      1 -total\n100.00%    4.461      1 Template:Ref\n 59.09%    2.636      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in pa